A urinal shaped like the puckered-up mouth of a woman waiting to be kissed is being installed in the men's room of the newly-opened Virgin Airways Clubhouse at Kennedy Airport.  John Riordan, customer-services vice president of the British airline, said the urinal should be a hit.  "We expect the response to the urinal to be very positive," he said.
